sources.title: I Know What I Saw (aka Post Mortem) | Full Movie | Crime Thriller | Beverley Mitchell
sources.description:
Mackenzie, an attractive and intelligent law student, is besieged by visions of murders she did not commit.  Traumatized by her father’s suicide and a messy breakup, things get even worse for Mackenzie when she accidentally hits a young woman with her car after a night out. By the time she summons help, the victim has disappeared-along with any evidence of her death. This is the beginning of a string of events that has Mackenzie questioning her own sanity, but as the violence intensifies, she struggles to solve the mystery before she or someone she loves winds up dead.
2007.  Stars: Beverley Mitchell, Geraint Wyn Davies, Chiara Zanni
